                            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Destination</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <li>• Santorini (Greek-themed village in Alaska)</li>
                                <li>• Spinalonga Island (Historic site replica)</li>
                                <li>• Melissani Cave (Crystal cave experience)</li>
                                <li>• Elafonissi Beach (Pink sand-inspired coastal walk)</li>
                                <li>• Museum Acropolis (Cultural center exhibit)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>


                        <div>
                            <h4 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Trip Details</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-600">
                                <li>• Duration: 5 Days 4 Nights</li>
                                <li>• Slots: 50 available</li>
                                <li>• Recommended Age: 12+</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
